data.description: Welcome home! This rarely available Pine Lake 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom beauty has been substantially remodeled! Stunning new wood look tile floors and completely remodeled bathrooms are just the beginning of the incredible features of this home. The open floor plan and sliders out to the pool make this house bright and inviting. Enjoy the best of south Florida living in your tropical back yard complete with an in-ground pool. Don't forget the 2-car garage, accordion shutters and whole house Generac generator! Notice the great curb appeal, with the newly painted exterior, double front doors and manicured lawn from the moment you pull up. No HOA. This house is truly move-in ready and will not last!
